{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-programs-js","path":"/programs/okta-sso-saml-setup.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>You can use your Okta credentials to sign in to HackerOne. To set up SSO via SAML for Okta:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Log in to Okta.</li>\n<li>Click the <b>Admin</b> button.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 483px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 26.400000000000002%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"okta admin button\"\n        title=\"okta admin button\"\n        src=\"/static/2192f9e0261720b5955b328c32828f62/77a9e/okta-1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/2192f9e0261720b5955b328c32828f62/fac75/okta-1.png 125w,\n/static/2192f9e0261720b5955b328c32828f62/63868/okta-1.png 250w,\n/static/2192f9e0261720b5955b328c32828f62/77a9e/okta-1.png 483w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 483px) 100vw, 483px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li>Click <b>+Add Application</b> under Shortcuts.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 354px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 114.39999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"okta shortcuts\"\n        title=\"okta shortcuts\"\n        src=\"/static/0492e1318e8a2ff63a532b80334eea73/8f50f/okta-2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/0492e1318e8a2ff63a532b80334eea73/fac75/okta-2.png 125w,\n/static/0492e1318e8a2ff63a532b80334eea73/63868/okta-2.png 250w,\n/static/0492e1318e8a2ff63a532b80334eea73/8f50f/okta-2.png 354w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 354px) 100vw, 354px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"4\">\n<li>Search for the HackerOne application and click <b>Add</b>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 19.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAAECAYAAACOXx+WAAAACXBIWXMAAAsSAAALEgHS3X78AAAAg0lEQVQY06WPSw5CMQhFu/8NugCntvb3Cv2kV6jWvPiGkpxAGBwuJueMUgqICGMM/FsmpowkUhWrtLX2pda6OIhhwwGWmZjBAp3gUzdEBdbalXILVNZ7XwdI9i5k3O4PhBDhfID/9Kewu+JjglGrc24Jt1Rfn3P+PDPXgev+XV1CaLgXVEE42ViDtWgAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"add HackerOne in okta\"\n        title=\"add HackerOne in okta\"\n        src=\"/static/f0583437c0e0ac3ab1b6524dff32ec1c/0b533/okta-3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/f0583437c0e0ac3ab1b6524dff32ec1c/fac75/okta-3.png 125w,\n/static/f0583437c0e0ac3ab1b6524dff32ec1c/63868/okta-3.png 250w,\n/static/f0583437c0e0ac3ab1b6524dff32ec1c/0b533/okta-3.png 500w,\n/static/f0583437c0e0ac3ab1b6524dff32ec1c/1d69c/okta-3.png 750w,\n/static/f0583437c0e0ac3ab1b6524dff32ec1c/00d43/okta-3.png 1000w,\n/static/f0583437c0e0ac3ab1b6524dff32ec1c/1843f/okta-3.png 1186w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"5\">\n<li>Select the options you'd like in your General Settings.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 51.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"okta general settings\"\n        title=\"okta general settings\"\n        src=\"/static/d522098bcad94f8be67aade223c0a120/0b533/okta-4.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d522098bcad94f8be67aade223c0a120/fac75/okta-4.png 125w,\n/static/d522098bcad94f8be67aade223c0a120/63868/okta-4.png 250w,\n/static/d522098bcad94f8be67aade223c0a120/0b533/okta-4.png 500w,\n/static/d522098bcad94f8be67aade223c0a120/1d69c/okta-4.png 750w,\n/static/d522098bcad94f8be67aade223c0a120/00d43/okta-4.png 1000w,\n/static/d522098bcad94f8be67aade223c0a120/09096/okta-4.png 2104w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"6\">\n<li>Click <b>Next</b>.</li>\n<li>Click <b>View Setup Instructions</b> on the Sing-On Options tab to open the \"How to Configure SAML 2.0 for HackerOne\" page. Keep this page open for setting up SAML for HackerOne in the later steps.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 67.19999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"okta saml 2.0\"\n        title=\"okta saml 2.0\"\n        src=\"/static/d84e8a8d42af76dd4b8b998d92bdb331/0b533/okta-5.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d84e8a8d42af76dd4b8b998d92bdb331/fac75/okta-5.png 125w,\n/static/d84e8a8d42af76dd4b8b998d92bdb331/63868/okta-5.png 250w,\n/static/d84e8a8d42af76dd4b8b998d92bdb331/0b533/okta-5.png 500w,\n/static/d84e8a8d42af76dd4b8b998d92bdb331/1d69c/okta-5.png 750w,\n/static/d84e8a8d42af76dd4b8b998d92bdb331/00d43/okta-5.png 1000w,\n/static/d84e8a8d42af76dd4b8b998d92bdb331/a6d66/okta-5.png 2070w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"8\">\n<li>Update the Credentials Details section and click <b>Done</b>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 48%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"okta credentials details\"\n        title=\"okta credentials details\"\n        src=\"/static/bd2d529bb5f04f23bad272ca61b1089f/0b533/okta-6.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bd2d529bb5f04f23bad272ca61b1089f/fac75/okta-6.png 125w,\n/static/bd2d529bb5f04f23bad272ca61b1089f/63868/okta-6.png 250w,\n/static/bd2d529bb5f04f23bad272ca61b1089f/0b533/okta-6.png 500w,\n/static/bd2d529bb5f04f23bad272ca61b1089f/1d69c/okta-6.png 750w,\n/static/bd2d529bb5f04f23bad272ca61b1089f/00d43/okta-6.png 1000w,\n/static/bd2d529bb5f04f23bad272ca61b1089f/2a08f/okta-6.png 1422w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"9\">\n<li>Assign the HackerOne application to the people or groups that should have access to the application on the Assignments tab.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 31.2%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"assign people/groups\"\n        title=\"assign people/groups\"\n        src=\"/static/95ffd81751ffd657e555da8b989b5adf/0b533/okta-7.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/95ffd81751ffd657e555da8b989b5adf/fac75/okta-7.png 125w,\n/static/95ffd81751ffd657e555da8b989b5adf/63868/okta-7.png 250w,\n/static/95ffd81751ffd657e555da8b989b5adf/0b533/okta-7.png 500w,\n/static/95ffd81751ffd657e555da8b989b5adf/1d69c/okta-7.png 750w,\n/static/95ffd81751ffd657e555da8b989b5adf/00d43/okta-7.png 1000w,\n/static/95ffd81751ffd657e555da8b989b5adf/66632/okta-7.png 1504w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<ol start=\"10\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.hackerone.com/\">Open HackerOne</a> in a new tab.</li>\n<li>Follow the SAML setup instructions <a href=\"/programs/single-sign-on-sso-via-saml.html\">here</a>.<br><ul><li>Copy the Single-Sign On URL and the X.509 Certificate from the “How to Configure SAML 2.0 for HackerOne” page 